metadata.name: OpenSeas
metadata.description:
OpenSeas is the Genesis photograph for JR's "Desirable Degen" Collection! The name "OpenSeas" plays directly off of the NFT platform "OpenSea". 

The shot was taken in Positano, Italy off the Amalfi Coast in August of 2022.

The owner of any 1/1 works from the Desirable Degen collection will receive monthly airdropped photographs as a show of appreciation for being one of his collectors.
